Welcome.Title: Introducing Quantler
Welcome.SubTitle: The tailor made alternative to traditional investement management
Welcome.H1Title: Now it's easy to automate your investing
Welcome.H1SubTitle: The first fully automated investing environment to align with your style of investing
Welcome.H1SubItem1Text: Choose from one of our many transparant community created quant funds, change them according to your believes or create one from scratch. The choices are endless.
Welcome.H1SubItem2Text: Whether you want to invest in a passive quant fund or on a speculative fashion, you are in control. Invest in equities, ETFs or crypto currencies.
Welcome.H1SubItem3Text: Do not agree with the way a quant fund works? Make any adjustments you want, all quant funds are open source. We have no closed doors.
Welcome.InvestInWhatYouBelieveIn: Invest in what you believe in

SmartFund.Title: Meet your personal investment fund
SmartFund.SubTitle: Invest using Quant Funds, which are digitalized investment funds. No pooled investments but fully customizable Quant Funds that fully allign with your interests.
SmartFund.H1Title: Every investor is unique, so is every quant fund.
SmartFund.H1SubTitle: Create or change an existing Quant Fund, in minutes
SmartFund.Text1: Universes, define what you want to trade on
SmartFund.Text3: Backtest and analyze its potential with the power of the cloud

General.Start: Start automating your investing. Invest where and what you want.
General.NoLockText: We stand behind our product and hosting service. At any time can you cancel your subscription for hosting your quant funds. Our software is open source, you are free to host your quant funds on other hosting providers as well.

FitStyle.Title: Fit to your style of investing
FitStyle.Text1: Fast quant funds hosted on low latency hosting facilities
FitStyle.Text2: Quant funds for analyzing many assets on a monthly or yearly basis

Hosting.Title: Host your Quant Fund at Quantler
Hosting.H1SubTitle: Quantler is all about flexibility and transperancy, all publicly available Quant Funds are open source and part of public domain (opposed to traditional investment management funds). You can host your Quant Fund wherever you want. Quantler's technical infrastructure is optimized for hosting your Quant Fund in a high quality, highly available and cost effective way.
Hosting.H2Title: Your Quant Funds, our technical expertise
Hosting.H2SubTitle: Create Quant Funds on themes such as Cyber Security, Connected Cars, Green Energy, Internet of Things
Hosting.WorksTitle: Here is how hosting a Quant Fund works

Hosting.WorksDeployText: Add or remove Quant Funds from your server
Hosting.WorksManageText: Review your Quant Fund's historical performance and optimize performance

FAQ.Title: What Can We Help You With?

q1.title: Where is Quantler regulated?
q1.description: Quantler is a software company based in the Netherlands. As a software company we focus on the technological aspect of investing, regulated activities are done by regulated financial instutions within selected jurisdictions. We, Quantler, are not a regulated entity.

q2.title: Is Quantler managing my funds?
q2.description: You are in total control of your own funds and since you are the creator, owner and sole investor of a Quant Fund, we (Quantler) do not provide any investment managament service.

q3.title: I live in country X, can I make use of Quantler?
q3.description: This depends on the broker you choose. If the broker allows you as a client, you can use our product with your brokerage account. Quantler, the platform, is available worldwide.

q4.title: What personal information do you need for opening an account?
q4.description: We need basic information such as your full name and where you live.

q1.title: How do I open a brokerage account?
q1.description: You cannot open a brokerage account at Quantler, for this we would like to forward you to the brokerage of your choosing. On the My Subscription page you can see the compatible brokers.

q2.title: Where can I find your source code?
q2.description: You can find our source code on github: https://github.com/Quantler/Core

q3.title: Are there any data related fees?
q3.description: No, we do not charge any additional fees for specific data. All data is available for all users on the platform.

Why.Title: Why Quantler?
Why.SubTitle: Creating a world where investing is alligned with the interests of the investor.
Why.H1Title: We eliminate costs, lower the barriers for access to investing and increase transparancy by making all investment decisions open source, eliminating any conflicts of interest that are associated with investment management today.
Why.BenefitsTitle: Some of the benefits of using Quantler
Why.BenefitsTextItem1: You are always in control, Quantler has no access to your funds. As we are a hosting company, we do not charge your for any trading activities.
Why.BenefitsTextItem2: Unlike pooled investments such as manual funds and exchange-traded funds (ETFs), when you use Quantler, you invest in what you want the way you want to do it
Why.BenefitsTextItem3: Quantler is open source, want to know how it works or improve it? At Quantler you can. We have nothing to hide, you can inspect investment decisions all the way.
Why.BenefitsTextItem4: Quantler is not a broker, it is a software company for automating your investing. You determine with who you want to invest with. Your not bound to a specific financial instution. Welcome to freedom of choice.

ICO.NotesText: Support us now by buying QUANT tokens, which will be needed for using our solution. Quant tokens are utility tokens used to fully utilize our platform. They have 3 main purposes: 1. it will be our only method of payment, 2. as a reward for mining when offering computational resources and 3. for incetivizing our open source community. In our whitepaper we explain our product on a higher level and explain the disruptive factor of our solution. Please check out our beta version for additional information regarding our product.
ICO.QUADCoinText: Quantler will only accept QUANT Tokens as method of payment for hosting Quant Funds. You can however, use many payment methods for acquiring these QUANT tokens, either from Quantler or elsewhere such as an exchange. QUANT tokens will be stored in a wallet at Quantler and fees will be automatically deducted using smart contracts on the Ethereum network.
ICO.SharesText: Run Quantler on your own machine and allow for incoming simulation requests (backtests). These simulations require a large amount of computational resources, miners are rewarded with Quant tokens for providing these resources.

FAQ.Title: Frequently asked questions
FAQ.A1: The QUANT token is a digital currency, used to fuel and support the Quantler ecosystem. Want to host a Quant Fund at Quantler? You will need QUANT tokens.
FAQ.Q2: How do I buy these QUANT tokens?
FAQ.A2: For the initial offering you will need to have ethereum to buy these QUANT tokens.
FAQ.Q3: Is the QUANT token a security?
FAQ.A3: The QUANT token will not grant you any voting nor dividend rights in Quantler B.V. (the company behind Quantler). The token is a utility token, as such it is not a security.
FAQ.Q4: Do I need to be whitelisted to buy these tokens?
FAQ.A4: During the initial token sale we will require every purchaser to whitelist him or herself. You can whitelist yourself in advance. Whitelisting involves providing your identity for KYC (Known Your Customer) and AML (Anti Money Laundering) processes. Both KYC and AML are only needed during the initial token sale, the use of our platform does not require any KYC/AML.
FAQ.Q5: Are there any restrictions in applying for the token sale?
FAQ.A5: Due to regulatory reasons, we will not accept participants from People's Republic of China, United States, South Korea and New Zealand. Other interested parties are welcomed to participate. QUANT Token is being developed as a utility token, and is not intended to be a security or regulated product in any jurisdiction, nor have we been reviewed by any regulatory authority. Anyone considering participation should assess the risks associated with digital assets and platforms.
